Class SourceCodeGraphFigure

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.draw2d.IFigure

    public class SourceCodeGraphFigure
extends com.drgarbage.draw2d.ControlFlowGraphFigure
    Embeded Control Flow Graph Viewer. It used for representation of method control flow graphs from a text editor. The nodes of the control flow graphs are synchronized with method lines in the text editor.
    Version:
    $Revision: 218 $ $Id: SourceCodeGraphFigure.java 1523 2012-04-13 14:34:24Z Sergej Alekseev $
